      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes use cases and documents call flows that require the History-Info header field to capture the Request-URIs as a Session Initiation Protocol (SIP) Request is retargeted.  The use cases are described along with the corresponding call flow diagrams and messaging details.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
